Changes
=======

0.02002 - Fri 26 May 2007
  - deps directory was missing. baaaah.

0.02001 - Fri 25 May 2007
  - require File::Temp >= 0.17, otherwise it does not inherit from IO::Seekable

0.02 - Thu 24 May 2007
  - Add missing methods: base(), is_success(), is_info(), is_redirect(),
    is_error(), decoded_contnet()
  - Add content_ref() for completeness, but this method raises an
    exception. You shouldn't be using this.
  - Make deps directory for optional dependencies
  - Properly use HTTP::Status, so that it doesn't clobber our namespace

0.01 - Thu 24 May 2007
  - Initial release.